    <p>It’s not too late to get your loved ones Christ­mas gifts, es­pe­cially with meet­ing num­bers still capped at five un­til De­cem­ber 28. These healthy cu­rated gift sets from Sin­ga­pore Food Shows (SFS) e-Shop con­tain food and bev­er­age items from around the world and are a great way to still show your ap­pre­ci­a­tion in the new year. The shop also car­ries over 1,000 prod­ucts and exclusive e-shop deals at up to 50 per cent off.</p>
    <p>For K-drama afi­ciona­dos, tr y a pack of Mem­o­ries scorched buck­wheat rice (300g) and a pack of Mem­o­ries scorched brown rice (1kg), now bun­dled at a pro­mo­tional price of $18.80 (U.P. $41.80), is an in­ter­est­ing gift. Al­ter­na­tively, cof­fee lovers among you will be de­lighted with JJ Royal The Hol­i­day Christ­mas Gift Set, which con­sists of a jute bag, three of their best­selling Kopi Tubruk cof­fee flavours, and Luwak Cof­fee in con­ve­nient drip fil­ters, $67.50 (U.P. $75).</p>
    <p>Those with young chil­dren will ap­pre­ci­ate the Lim­ited Edi­tion HaruBlox Christ­mas Gift Set ($32), cre­ated by lo­cal com­pany HaruPlate. It con­tains one chunky ap­ple jam (100g), one tango mango jam (100g), one blue­berr y pear jam (100g) and one tomato sam­bal (100g) in a cute Christ­mas pack­ag­ing. The sweet jams are nat­u­rally made with real fruits and can be en­joyed on toast, while the non-spicy tomato sam­bal can be used in kid-friendly nasi lemak and pasta.</p>
    <p>And for those whom you are not able to meet un­til next year due to Covid-19 restrictio­ns on gath­er­ings, pre­mium truf­fle gift sets from Europe sent to their doorstep can help you ex­press that they’re still im­por tant to you. A set of three truf­fle condi­ments in honey, mus­tard and sea salt flavours in a classy black box costs $45.90. Browse other gift sets on the site that pack­age black and white truf­fle oil, as well as white truf­fle bal­samic vine­gar in con­ve­nient gift boxes.</p>
    <p>Make sure to use the new user promo codes ‘XMAS50’ for $5 off $10 spent, or ‘XMAS10’ for 10 per cent off your first pur­chase.</p>


